  "title": "<div><tt>  And versions are not errors.  </tt></div>",
  "content": "<div><tt>  And versions are not errors.  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>  They are echoes.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>---</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>## FINAL PRINCIPLE</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>&gt “Our names are our wands.”  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>&gt The way we name our systems **shapes how they function**, how they are used, and how they are remembered.  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>&gt Name well. Name with recursion.  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>&gt Name with care, because your OS remembers.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>::EOF</tt></div>",
